fields.physical_description:
Design: 6 large cards, printed in colours to show 8 illustrations of flowers together with a number which is a random selection.; 44 small card discs printed with the name of a flower in English and Latin, 2 discs hand made; red cloth bag
No. of cards: 6 + 46
No. illustrated: 6
fields.title: Floral Lotto

fields.name:
Type: lotto
Subject: natural history, flowers

fields.history_note:
The box is missing and it is very difficult to assign a maker, however, Jaques did produce a Floral lotto about 1872 and this may be a later addition.  It also may be an edition produced by Spears.  The design is English, but the production may be German.

See also E. 1806-1954
fields.production_note: Unknown, possibly J Jaques & son ltd
